apps.name: Youtube (Cercube+Extra)
apps.subtitle: Cercube with extra features!
apps.versionDescription:
Current YouTube IPA: "v18.22.9"
Current Cercube Version: "v5.3.11"
Current App Compatibility: "iOS/iPadOS 14.0" or later

RELEASE F1: (June 6th 2023)
• Updated YouTube from "v18.20.3" to "v18.22.9"
• Updated LowContrastMode (arichorn)
   • Added "UILabel" Support
   • Added "ASyncDisplayKit" Support
• Added Submodules
   • YTHoldForSpeed
      • add a tweak that adds a hold gesture on the video player to quickly toggle the playback speed.
   • DontEatMyContent
      • a tweak that removes Dynamic Island/Notch on specific devices
• Updated Submodules
   • iSponsorBlock v1.1.2
     • Fixed Icons not appearing
     • Added Changeable iSponsorBlock API
     • Added Changeable iSponsorBlock User ID
     • Bug Fixes (etc)
   • YTUHD v1.4.0
     • Improvements
     • Bug Fixes (etc)

Issues in this Release:

• Options “Enable Share Button” & “Enable ‘Save to Playlist’ Button” don’t work correctly.
• [Cercube Exclusive] • Cercube Download Tab & Cercube Menu not working with YouTube's New Dark Mode
• Live Videos/Streams Crashing / Live Chat Messages Invisible (39)
• Hide Shorts Videos not working Correctly (38)
• OLED/OLD Dark Theme Options Not Working (Workaround: use this version of CercubePlusExtra: v18.20.3•5.3.11)
apps.localizedDescription:
Cercube with extra features! 

Supercharge your YouTube experience with +15 tweaks: 

• Cercube: Ad-blocking & background playback
• iSponsorBlock: Skip sponsor ads
• YouPiP: Native PiP mode
• YTUHD: 2K & 4K video quality
• YouTube Dislike Return: Reinstate dislike counts
• YTClassicVideoQuality: Old video quality selector
• YTNoHoverCards: Disable suggested videos
• YTABGoodies: Disable A/B testing features
• NOYTPremium: Remove Premium upsell alerts
• YTSpeed: Add 2.25x to 4x playback speeds
• YTMiniplayerEnabler: Enable Miniplayer
• DontEatMyContent: Prevent notch issues
• YTShortsProgress: Enable progress bar for Shorts
• YTABConfig: Control A/B testing flags
• YouMute: Mute/unmute videos
• LowContrastMode: Reduce interface contrast
• And many more...
